OL,3,CCanadian university scraps Guernsey
OL,4,Cscholarship
OL,6,FStudents in Guernsey will no longer
OL,7,Fhave the chance to study for free in
OL,8,FCanada, after Brock University has
OL,9,Fannounced they will be discontinuing
OL,10,Ftheir annual scholarship for young
OL,11,Fpeople from the island.
OL,13,FFor decades, Brock University in
OL,14,FOntario has offered a fully-funded
OL,15,Facademic scholarship to one graduating
OL,16,FGuernsey student each year. The aim is
OL,17,Fto give them the chance to travel and
OL,18,Fexperience a unique educational
OL,19,Fopportunity for a fraction of what it
OL,20,Fmight typically cost them to study
OL,21,Fabroad.
