OL,6,FThe scheme was set up in honour of
OL,7,Ftheir namesake, Major-General Sir
OL,8,FIsaac Brock, a Guernsey-born British
OL,9,FArmy Officer who is remembered across
OL,10,FCanada as a hero of the War of 1812.
OL,12,FHowever, the University has decided to
OL,13,Fscrap the scholarship after being
OL,14,Fforced to reconsider its finances and
OL,15,Fpriorities.
