OL,6,FThe University's Associate Vice-
OL,7,FPresident, David Begg says the
OL,8,FUniversity continues to value its
OL,9,Fclose relationship with the island,
OL,10,Fand "does not take the discontinuation
OL,11,Fof this scholarship lightly.
OL,13,F"The decision was made as part of a
OL,14,Fbroader evaluation of institutional
OL,15,Fpriorities and fiscal planning", he
OL,16,Fadds.
