OL,3,CCanadian university scraps Guernsey
OL,4,Cscholarship
OL,6,FHe further notes the University will
OL,7,Fcontinue to welcome Guernsey students
OL,8,Fthrough their typical admissions
OL,9,Fprocess, which leaves some scholarship
OL,10,Fand funding options open to them.
OL,12,FFor islanders, these options include
OL,13,Fthe merit-based 'Brock Scholars
OL,14,FAward', 'International Curriculum
OL,15,FAward', and the 'Brock Global Reach
OL,16,FAward'.
OL,18,FNone of these options, however, cover
OL,19,Fthe full cost of tuition.
