OL,6,FGuernsey's President for Education,
OL,7,FSport, and Culture, Deputy Paul
OL,8,FMontague, says the department is
OL,9,F"disappointed" to hear of Brock's
OL,10,Fdecision to end the scheme, but
OL,11,F"understands the pressures affecting
OL,12,Funiversity globally".
OL,14,FHowever, he adds "at the same time, it
OL,15,Fis also a challenging financial
OL,16,Flandscape for our students and
OL,17,Ffamilies.
