OL,6,F"The Committee is reviewing how we
OL,7,Fsupport access to higher education
OL,8,Fopportunities at home and elsewhere,
OL,9,Fto ensure higher education is
OL,10,Faccessible as possible and aligned
OL,11,Fwith the evolving opportunities
OL,12,Favailable".
OL,14,FThe four scholars currently studying
OL,15,Fat Brock University will not be
OL,16,Faffected by the changes and will
OL,17,Fcontinue to receive their awarded
OL,18,Ftuition fees until their graduations.
